= SDIFF _key1_ _key2_ ... _keyN_ =
_Time complexity O(N) with N being the total number of elements of all the sets_

 Return the members of a set resulting from the difference between the first
 set provided and all the successive sets.

 Non existing keys are considered like empty sets.

== Return value ==

[ReplyTypes Multi bulk reply], specifically the list of common elements.
